Title: DEVELOPMENT
Action: Each player can develop a product
Privilege: The activity initiator can develop an additional product

Title: DEPLOYMENT
Action: Each player can deploy a product
Privilege: The activity initiator can deploy an additional product

Title: RETROSPECTIVE
Action: Each player can set up a team, an action or a value
Privilege: The activity initiator pays one card less

Title: CONFERENCE
Action: Each player draws two cards and keep one
Privilege: The activity initiator draws five cards instead of two

Title: COACH
Action: The coach intervention is limited to the activity initiator
Privilege: The activity initiator draws one card and keep it
